prompt: Summarize the following story in first person: So the story I want to tell you about would be my adventure about trying to get my son into school. Into a good school that is. He was going to have to go to a school district that was not safe at all and one that me and my wife did not want him to have to go to. We really needed him to get into the school in to the right one.  So we decided that the only course of action would be for us to move. That of course is a lot easier said than done.
